# Phase 33: Creator Revenue Dashboard & Vantix zk Integration

This phase focuses on surfacing the Phase 32 payment data to creators and adding a "Proof of Humanity" layer using Vantix zk technology to ensure all tips and engagement are bot-proof.

## Proposed Changes

### [Revenue Dashboard]
#### [MODIFY] [DashboardClient.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/studio/dashboard/DashboardClient.tsx)
- Add a "Revenue" tab to the Creator Studio.
- Implement a high-fidelity "Earnings Overview" card showing total USDC/Native tips.
- Add a "Recent Tips" table fetching from the `tip_transactions` table created in Phase 32.
- Integrate Recharts/Lucide for visual velocity charts (tips over time).

### [Vantix zk Integration]
#### [NEW] [VantixProvider.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/components/VantixProvider.tsx)
- Integrate [Vantix.xyz](https://vantix.xyz) SDK or API for zk-proof "Is Human" verification.
- Wrap the app to provide a global `isVerifiedHuman` state.

#### [MODIFY] [TipButton.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/components/TipButton.tsx)
- Add a "Bot-Proof Verified" badge to the tip modal.
- Optional: Require a Vantix zk-proof before allowing a tip (configurable by creator).

### [Analytics Backend]
#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///C:/GOLive/app/api/studio/revenue/route.ts)
- Aggregated API endpoint to fetch transaction data for the dashboard.
- Calculate 24h/7d revenue growth.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Test sub-second fetch of `tip_transactions` for a creator.
- Verify 75/25 calculation accuracy in dashboard display.

### Manual Verification
- Perform a test tip (Sepolia/Devnet) and verify it appears in the dashboard instantly via Supabase real-time or refresh.
- Trigger a Vantix zk-check and verify "Verified Human" badge appears.
